Title: MANIFOLD COMPOSITIONS, MUSIC VISUALIZATION, AND SCIENTIFIC SONIFICATION IN AN IMMERSIVE VIRTUAL-REALITY ENVIRONMENT  
Author: Hans G. Kaper 
